    {
      "parameters": {
        "formTitle": "Job Application Form",
        "formDescription": "AI Automation Engineer – Job Description\nJob Title:\n\nAI Automation Engineer\n\nJob Summary:\n\nWe are looking for an AI Automation Engineer to design, develop, and maintain intelligent automation solutions that streamline business processes and improve operational efficiency. The ideal candidate will have experience with workflow automation tools, AI technologies, API integrations, and process optimization.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\nDesign and implement AI-powered automation workflows.\nDevelop and maintain automations using tools such as n8n, Make, Zapier, or similar platforms.\nIntegrate AI models (OpenAI, Claude, Gemini, etc.) into business processes.\nBuild and manage API integrations, webhooks, and third-party services.\nAutomate repetitive tasks across departments such as HR, Sales, Operations, and Marketing.\nCreate AI agents, chatbots, and automated communication systems.\nMonitor, troubleshoot, and optimize automation workflows.\nCollaborate with stakeholders to identify automation opportunities.\nDocument workflows, processes, and technical solutions.\nEnsure automation systems are secure, scalable, and reliable.\nRequired Skills:\nExperience with workflow automation platforms (n8n, Zapier, Make).\nKnowledge of LLMs (Large Language Models) and Prompt Engineering.\nExperience with REST APIs, Webhooks, and integrations.\nBasic programming knowledge in JavaScript or Python.\nUnderstanding of AI tools and automation frameworks.\nFamiliarity with databases, Google Workspace, Slack, and productivity tools.\nStrong analytical and problem-solving skills.\nPreferred Skills:\nAI Agent Development\nRAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)\nVector Databases\nLangChain or similar frameworks\nCloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP)\nPhotoshop Automation or Process Automation experience\nQualifications:\nBachelor's degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, ECE, or related field.\n1+ years of experience in Automation, AI, or Software Development.\nTools & Technologies:\nn8n\nOpenAI API\nGoogle Sheets\nSlack\nGmail\nJavaScript\nPython\nREST APIs\nGitHub\nWebhooks",
